{"tid":2332685,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【送比世界各地既手足】  有一種既信仰，叫「香港人」。","createTime":"2020-12-19T20:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T12:46:28.000Z","uid":154486,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb70fe8c1ab24bd7757610313818718a21b3eee1","tid":2332685,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"之前見到良善巴既Post：<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>香港人呢一刻需要嘅係一種「信仰」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2266669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2266669</a></strong> </span><br />\n加埋岩岩睇完個網上音樂會，聽左首歌「最後的信仰」，所以有少少感觸想講下<br />\n<ins>本身良善巴係Post入面貼既係「煲底之約」四格漫畫</ins>，相信大家都睇過<br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得呢一篇係2015年出現既漫畫，好適合係呢個時候比大家重溫：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMNiNP2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMNiNP2.png&h=1b016f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B9mjxgE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB9mjxgE.png&h=b07f2e8f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hP8Rooj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhP8Rooj.png&h=4ec7934c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WZExgF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WZExgF.png&h=c850092b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Moek090.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoek090.png&h=5b4b99af&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5Mb7P1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5Mb7P1.png&h=d027e1cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENVcSgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENVcSgG.png&h=f95bad46&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLzMWJn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLzMWJn.png&h=fc9c1ecc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">「香港人」呢一個民族<br />\n<ins>就係我地既信仰</ins>。</span></span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n當然漫畫內容係誇大左（畢竟係2015年作品）<br />\n有香港身分證都唔代表你係香港人<br />\n我都好希望唔需要等幾世紀<br />\n但係漫畫個Message已經好清楚：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><p class=\"center\">就算冇左香港呢個地方，我地都係香港人。<br />\nHong Kong is not a place, is a People.</p></strong></span><br />\n良善巴既原Post入面提及張可森「以香港作為信仰」既理念<br />\n主要係解釋信仰同煲底見既關係<br />\n我絕對支持佢既論點，但係我想再補充一點：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「香港」呢個地方（22&deg;18&rsquo;13&rdquo;N，114&deg;10&rsquo;19&rdquo;E），冇錯可能已經玩完<br />\n但係「香港人」呢個民族既存亡<br />\n其實就係你我既一念之間。</strong><br />\n大家出世冇記認<br />\n放棄信仰，放棄身份其實好容易<br />\n你可以攞住唔同既國籍，講唔同既語言，唔係香港出世<br />\n或者只要講一聲：<br />\n「我係中國人」&quot;I am Chinese&quot;<br />\n就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n經過左咁多年既跌跌撞撞<br />\n<strong>由以前既反雙非、反蝗、反水貨走私、集體回憶<br />\n到之後既香港人優先、雨傘革命、本土思潮、本民前、民族論、青政、民族黨<br />\n最後到反送中，到而家呢個環境</strong><br />\n<ins>無數前人犧牲左自己最寶貴既時間、人力、心機、自由甚至性命</ins><br />\n為大家係共匪大軍壓境前一刻，預先行到呢一步<br />\n但係雖然香港人既身份看似堅不可摧<br />\n你我都要承認<br />\n<strong>去摧毀、否定或者改造自己既歷史同身份，其實可以好簡單</strong><br />\n<br />\n無論係大家抗爭既目的係為左乜野<br />\n所有野既大前提<br />\n<strong>就係要係本地或者外國默默保存香港民族既精神火種</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>不論你係<br />\n順民、暴民、移民<br />\n都請你係心入面堅持呢兩句話：<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><br />\n「我係香港民族既一份子」<br />\n「我係香港人」 </p><br />\n</strong>孟子話：「天將降大任於斯人也，必先苦其心志，勞其筋骨，餓其體膚，空乏其身，行拂亂其所為，所以動心忍性，增益其所不能」 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>世界上所有現存既民族都面對過自己既苦難，一個民族流離失所係等閒之事<br />\n係呢Ｄ苦難中煉成左既堅毅與盼望，最後就會成為一個國家精神既雛型</strong><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">「香港人」呢個民族既試煉，冇人知道會有幾難捱，冇人知要幾耐<br />\n但係我地唯一可以做既<br />\n就係<strong>相信香港人既力量</strong><br />\n以及<strong>相信組成「香港人」身份既呢三樣野：價值觀、生活方式、人生意義</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mjw665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mjw665.jpg&h=f976602b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種相信，就係由世界各地既流亡者，以及係香港既人一齊默默守護既<br />\n呢一種稱之為「香港人」既信仰<br />\n<br />\n<strong>願榮光係我地既詩歌<br />\n香港係我地既聖地<br />\n民主自由係我地既教義<br />\n光復香港係我地既任務<br />\n世界各地既香港人團體就係我地既教會<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9rzmKO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9rzmKO.jpg&h=0090b085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>All-In Hong Kong. Hong Kong In All. </strong></span></p>"},{"pid":"5556e5b8e979989722fb5e9f35f9f9dd8149e132","tid":2332685,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:04:00.000Z","msg":"title打多左個既字<br />\n算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37786dfc1aa3939e7fabfa64ea6b460988196097","tid":2332685,"uid":44019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:04:50.000Z","msg":"We are Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"908f32db64aa246cafafcbfb312d02dc5c931c5a","tid":2332685,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0adf7e17f4c502e3efaaeb3e9ec1c8af4817d5a","tid":2332685,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:08:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c268812ac03b723d3aa820786bf7191e1cca94b","tid":2332685,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37786dfc1aa3939e7fabfa64ea6b460988196097","tid":2332685,"uid":44019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:04:50.000Z","msg":"We are Hong Kong!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地而家做既，講既每一樣野<br />\n就係後代心目中、口中既「香港」<br />\n<br />\n責任好大架，大家要比心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2259d72a39c7c6e5f2fdf2d3ea60cbde8aa18ebf","tid":2332685,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:09:36.000Z","msg":"<i